BARNARD v. GANTZ et al. (Supreme Court, General Term, Second Department. May 14, 1894.) Action by John T. Barnard, as temporary administrator, etc., of Ann E. Crouse, against John F. Gantz and others.

Argued before BROWN, P. J, and DYKMAN and CULLEN. JJ.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with costs. See 21 N. Y. Supp. 349; 23 N. Y. Supp. 260.
